滚石乐队确认新专辑“Hackney Diamonds”和单曲“Angry” https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-rolling-stones-confirm-new-album-hackney-diamonds-and-single-angry-3494112?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-rolling-stones-确认新专辑哈克尼钻石和单身愤怒Damian JonesWed, 06 Sep 2023 13:57:56 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3494112 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_rollingstones_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="哈克尼的滚石乐队，" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_rollingstones_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_rollingstones_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_rollingstones_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_rollingstones_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_rollingstones_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_rollingstones_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>吉米·法伦 (Jimmy Fallon) 在 YouTube 直播中采访了乐队有关新唱片的事宜</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-rolling-stones-confirm-new-album-hackney-diamonds-and-single-angry-3494112">滚石乐队确认新专辑“Hackney Diamonds”和单曲“Angry”</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_rollingstones_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="哈克尼的滚石乐队，" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_rollingstones_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_rollingstones_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_rollingstones_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_rollingstones_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_rollingstones_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_rollingstones_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-rolling-stones">滚石乐队</a>正式宣布了他们的新专辑“Hackney Diamonds”，并分享了新单曲“Angry”的详细信息。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/rolling-stone-songs-10-best-2263181">滚石乐队 – 他们最好的 10 首歌曲</a></strong></li></ul><p>本周早些时候，这支老牌摇滚乐队的第 24 张唱片在一份新闻稿中被确认为他们自 2005 年的《A Bigger Bang》以来的第一张原创音乐。</p><p>今天下午（9 月 6 日），乐队成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mick-jagger">米克·贾格尔 (Mick Jagger)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/keith-richards">基思·理查兹 (Keith Richards</a> ) 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ronnie-wood">罗尼·伍德 (Ronnie Wood)</a>在哈克尼帝国 (Hackney Empire) 的直播中与主持人<em>吉米·法伦 (Jimmy Fallon) 主演的《今夜秀》(The Tonight Show Starring</em> Jimmy Fallon) 谈论了这张新唱片。</p><p>米克·贾格尔在透露新专辑时说道：“我们来这里是为了展示我们的新单曲《Angry》和新视频。我们的新专辑《Hackney Diamonds》也将于 10 月 20 日发行。”您可以观看下面由<em>《Euphoria》</em>女演员西德尼·斯威尼 (Sydney Sweeney) 主演的视频。 </p><p><iframe title="滚石乐队 - 愤怒（官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/_mEC54eTuGw?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “我们必须制作一张我们真正爱自己的唱片，”贾格尔在谈到乐队这张专辑的目标时补充道。 “我们对此感到满意，我希望你们也感到满意。”</p><p>他还确认新唱片有 12 首曲目，其中两首是由前鼓手 Charlie Watts 创作的，乐队于 2022 年底开始制作新歌曲，目标是在 2023 年中期完成专辑。</p><p>您现在可以在下面观看现场直播。 </p><p><iframe title="滚石乐队现场对话吉米·法伦" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/NSzJhzfDtS4?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>上个月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-rolling-stones-appear-to-announce-new-album-hackney-diamonds-in-local-newspaper-3486819">，这张新唱片似乎是通过当地报纸上的一则神秘广告宣布的</a>，而上周<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-rolling-stones-tease-hackney-diamonds-announcement-fuelling-album-rumours-3492244">乐队则通过增强现实视频剪辑和网站戏弄了全球范围内的“Hackney Diamonds”公告</a>。</p><p>他们还通过一个名为<a href="https://www.dontgetangrywithme.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">dontgetangrywithme.com</a>的网站<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-rolling-stones-tease-snippet-of-new-song-angry-3492586">预告了他们的新单曲“Angry”的片段</a>。</p><p> “哈克尼可能是哈克尼钻石的核心，但这是一个真正的全球时刻，我们希望通过 YouTube 与世界各地的粉丝分享，”滚石乐队在有关该活动的声明中表示。</p><p>滚石乐队的上一张专辑是蓝调翻唱唱片《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/rolling-stones-blue-lonesome-1882686#:~:text=These%2012%20tracks%20were%20recorded,but%20not%20wanting%20for%20thrills.">Blue &amp; Lonesome</a> 》（2016 年）。</p><p>与此同时，主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mick-jagger">米克·贾格尔</a>最近庆祝了他的80岁生日，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/keith-richards">基思·理查兹</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ronnie-wood">罗尼·伍德</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists.nile-rodgers">尼罗·罗杰斯</a>都<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/keith-richards-leads-80th-birthday-wishes-to-mick-jagger-3473780">送上了最美好的祝福</a>。</p><p> “Hackney Diamonds”的完整曲目列表如下：</p><p> <strong>&#39;生气的&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;靠近&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>“取决于你”</strong><br /> <strong>“咬掉我的头”</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;整个世界&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>《梦幻的天空》</strong><br /> <strong>“搞砸了”</strong><br /> <strong>《靠剑生存》</strong><br /> <strong>“让我太难受了”</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;直接告诉我</strong><br /><strong>《天堂的甜蜜声音》</strong><br /> <strong>《滚石蓝调》</strong></p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-rolling-stones-confirm-new-album-hackney-diamonds-and-single-angry-3494112">滚石乐队确认新专辑“Hackney Diamonds”和单曲“Angry”</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
文斯·克拉克 (Vince Clarke) 宣布推出首张个人专辑，并分享主打单曲《耶利米哀歌》(The Lamentations Of Jeremiah) https://www.nme.com/news/music/vince-clarke-announces-debut-solo-album-shares-lead-single-the-lamentations-of-jeremiah-3493973?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=vince-克拉克宣布首张个人专辑共享主打单曲《耶利米哀歌》Liberty Dunworth Wed, 06 Sep 2023 13:45:12 +0000 Music NewsNewsAlternative https://www.nme.com/?p=3493973 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Vince-Clarke@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Vince-Clarke@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Vince-Clarke@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Vince-Clarke@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Vince-Clarke@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Vince-Clarke@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Vince-Clarke@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 《沉默之歌》将于今年晚些时候发行</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/vince-clarke-announces-debut-solo-album-shares-lead-single-the-lamentations-of-jeremiah-3493973">文斯·克拉克 (Vince Clarke) 宣布推出首张个人专辑，并分享主打单曲《耶利米哀歌》(The Lamentations Of Jeremiah)，该专辑</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Vince-Clarke@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Vince-Clarke@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Vince-Clarke@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Vince-Clarke@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Vince-Clarke@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Vince-Clarke@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Vince-Clarke@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/erasure">Erasure</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yazoo">Yazoo</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/depeche-mode">Depeche Mode</a>等乐队创作的词曲作者文斯·克拉克 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/vince-clarke">Vince Clarke</a> ) 宣布了他的首张个人专辑《Songs Of Silence》的详细信息。看看下面的主打单曲。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/depeche-mode-rank-the-albums-766535">Depeche Mode：每张专辑的排名和评级</a><br /></strong></li></ul><p>即将于 11 月 17 日通过 Mute 发行的这张器乐专辑将让艾弗·诺韦洛 (Ivor Novello) 获奖歌曲作者探索 Eurorack 的无限可能性——这是一种模块化合成器格式，以其令人上瘾和无限的配置而闻名。</p><p>据一份新闻稿称，这也让克拉克能够探索音乐流派的前提，创造出比他无数排行榜冠军专辑更具实验性的唱片，并开发出“一张包含无法分类的环境美的 10 首歌曲的无歌词专辑”。</p><p>看看下面的主打单曲“耶利米哀歌”，它配有由土耳其出生的纽约肖像摄影师 Ebru Yildiz 执导的视觉伴奏。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="视频" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/OQK95AtGi0U?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “我本可以永远继续下去，我本可以不停歇，”克拉克在解释他在为专辑创作新材料时使用 Eurorack 时说道。</p><p> “我非常享受这个过程，并没有考虑其他人听到它。但听到它在我的工作室里在我的脑海中发展，学习新的技巧——这就是最好的事情。事实上，当 Mute 说他们想发行这张专辑时，我感到很震惊。” </p><figure id="attachment_3493982" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3493982" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3493982" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Vince-Clarke_Songs-of-Silence_artwork@2000x2000.jpg" alt="文斯·克拉克，《沉默之歌》艺术作品" width="2000" height="2004" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Vince-Clarke_Songs-of-Silence_artwork@2000x2000.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Vince-Clarke_Songs-of-Silence_artwork@2000x2000-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Vince-Clarke_Songs-of-Silence_artwork@2000x2000-400x401.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Vince-Clarke_Songs-of-Silence_artwork@2000x2000-800x802.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Vince-Clarke_Songs-of-Silence_artwork@2000x2000-696x697.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Vince-Clarke_Songs-of-Silence_artwork@2000x2000-1392x1395.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Vince-Clarke_Songs-of-Silence_artwork@2000x2000-1068x1070.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3493982" class="wp-caption-text">文斯·克拉克，《沉默之歌》艺术作品。图片来源：尤金·理查兹/出版社</figcaption></figure><p>这张专辑也是在他位于纽约的家庭录音室录制的，最初是在封锁期间作为一种创造性的消遣。克拉克还遵循两条规则：第一条是专辑生成的声音将主要来自 Eurorack，第二条是每首歌都以一个音符为中心，始终保持一个调。</p><p> “由此产生的专辑的合成器生成的、宇宙遥远的情绪被鲜明的干预所打断，提醒人们在这台机器中工作的人手，”新闻稿中描述了专辑的整体声音。 “Clarke 展现了无情的音序器模式、逐渐加速、Moog 风格的嗡嗡声、闪闪发光的合成水滴以及经过处理的吉他的迅速膨胀，Clarke 将这些曲目描述为“有一种悲伤、事情变坏、事情崩溃的感觉”。</p><p> <a href="https://mute.ffm.to/vinceclarke_sos%22%20%5Co%20%22https://mute.ffm.to/vinceclarke_sos" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处</a>进行预订并查看下面专辑的曲目列表。</p><h3> <strong>《沉默之歌》曲目列表</strong></h3><p><strong>1.“大教堂”</strong><br /> <strong>2.《白兔》</strong><br /> <strong>3.“通道”</strong><br /> <strong>4.“迫在眉睫”</strong><br /> <strong>5.“红色星球”</strong><br /> <strong>6.《耶利米哀歌》</strong><br /> <strong>7.“有丝分裂”</strong><br /> <strong>8.“黑腿”</strong><br /> <strong>9.“斯卡珀”</strong><br /> <strong>10.“最后一次传输”</strong></p><p>在 Vince Clarke 的其他新闻中，早在 2019 年，这位音乐家就分享了他在与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/omd">OMD</a>合作时发现了自己对合成器的部分热爱，OMD<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/vince-clarke-erasure-remix-omd-almost-2551457">分享了歌曲“Almost”的混音版</a>。</p><p> “OMD 说服我改用合成器，”他当时说道，“我想‘我能做到。我可以写那样的歌。”</p><p>此外，继今年早些时候 Depeche Mode 发行第 15 张录音室专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/depeche-mode-memento-mori-review-3418286">《Memento Mori》</a>后， <em>NME</em>分享了<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/depeche-mode-rank-the-albums-766535">该乐队最佳专辑的倒计时</a>。</p><p>在这里，1990 年代的《Violator》位居榜首， <em>《NME》</em>将其描述为呈现出“一种与以往一样舒适的模式——仍然能够像《Enjoy The Silence》和《Policy》那样流行开瓶器。 Of Truth”，但在“Halo”和“Sweetest Perfection”中磨练了他们怪异、具有威胁性的民谣。”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/vince-clarke-announces-debut-solo-album-shares-lead-single-the-lamentations-of-jeremiah-3493973">文斯·克拉克 (Vince Clarke) 宣布推出首张个人专辑，并分享主打单曲《耶利米哀歌》(The Lamentations Of Jeremiah)，该专辑</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
